<aside class="sidebar">
  
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <!-- About BubbleCow -->
    <h2 class="sidebar__section-title">About <%= bubblecow_name %></h2>
    <p>BubbleCow's goal is to provide world-class editorial feedback and customer support, at a price that is affordable to self-published writers.</p>
    <p>BubbleCow is an editing company that was born into the modern world of self-publishing. We have developed a way of editing that not only shows you whatâ€™s wrong with your book but gives you all the guidance you need to fix the mistakes.</p>
    <p>For us, the quality of the feedback is everything.</p>
    <%= link_to "Learn more about our story here...", about_path %>
  </div>

  <!-- Free courses -->
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <h3 class="sidebar__section-title">Free Courses</h3>
    <p>We provide a range of free courses to help writers. Just create a free account to get started.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "All Courses", courses_path %></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Free eBooks -->
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <h3 class="sidebar__section-title">Free eBooks</h3>
    <p>The best way to learn is by doing. FOR FREE you can get tried and tested guidence just by studying these guides. They're here for you.</p>
    <ul>
        <li><%= link_to "The Writing Manual", "https://bubblecow.com/writing_manual" %></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Categories -->
  <div class="sidebar__section">
    <h3 class="sidebar__section-title">Catergories</h3>
    <p>Turning your book into a success requires great writing and great book marketing. Here's some articles that will help you get started: </p>
    <ul>
      <% @categories.where(parent_category_id: nil).order(:name).each do |parent_category| %>
        <li>
          <%= link_to parent_category.name.titleize, blog_post_category_path(parent_category) %>
          <% if parent_category.child_categories.any? %>
            <ul>
              <% parent_category.child_categories.order(:name).each do |child_category| %>
                <li><%= link_to child_category.name.titleize, blog_post_category_path(child_category) %></li>
              <% end %>
            </ul>
          <% end %>
        </li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>

  </div>

</aside>